LYRICS:

Tu hi torhi si
Majboori thorhi si
Main rokya si tenu
Teri gal tu morhi si
Torhan vele gal da vi mauka tu nai dita
Aeh koi gal banndi hai hun milna tu chahuni hain
Aape chadya si tu mainu ohde karke ni
Ohdi hoke hun tu mainu phone kyun launi hain

Main tan khush han ki kraan j hun tu khush nahi
Tu mere lyi ex ton vadhke hun tan kuch nahi
Chalo chalo hun hato ji
Mitti na patto ji
Hun koi fayda nahi
Tusi phone nu katto ji
Tere lyi story koi hun nahi paayidi
Tere matlab da nai kuch jo dekhan aundi hain
Aape chadya si tu mainu ohde karke ni
Ohdi hoke hun tu mainu phone kyun launi hain

Mere kyun iraade tenu kache lagde si
Asi pyar jataunde si tan tenu bache lagde si
Ache deve
Mann ke sache deve
Aehi keh sakde han rabb
Thonu bache deve
Changa bhala hai agla tera dil ton karda hou
Kaahton oh bichaara bevakuuf banaundi hain

Rukjo main auni han
Ohda pyar sikhauni han
Ik vaari meri gal karaao
Ohnu main hatauni han
Changa ji tusi khush raho par apne ghar raho
Mainu pyari jhi nu kyu tu gussa charhaundi hain

Aape chadya si tu aehnu ohde karke ni
Ohdi hoke hun tu aehnu phone kyun launi hain

snippet.title: Rapper Mo3 shot dead on Dallas highway
snippet.description:
DALLAS - Rapper Mo3 was shot dead on a Dallas highway on Wednesday, sources tell FOX4.

The rapper, whose real name was Melvin Noble, was killed midday in an incident on northbound Interstate 35 near Clarendon Drive.

Dallas police declined to publicly confirm the rapper, 28, was killed in the shooting, but did release a narrative of the incident.

Police said he was in a vehicle on I-35 just before noon when a suspect approached Mo3’s car.

Both men stopped their vehicles, the victim got out and started running but was shot several times on the highway.

A bystander inside another vehicle was struck as well. Police say that person did not suffer life threatening injuries.

Police are still looking for the shooter of the Dallas-based rapper.

Video circulating on social media purports to show Mo3 lying on the highway as someone tries to help him after being shot.

Mo3 had previously said that he was the victim of a non-fatal 2019 shooting.

Mo3’s most notable hit was "Errybody (Remix),” collaboration with Boosie Badazz. 

FOX 4 News is a FOX-owned station serving Dallas-Fort Worth and all of North Texas.

snippet.title: Xbox Series X Unboxing & 48 Hour Review | A Mixed Bag!
snippet.description:
Xbox Series X Unboxing & 48 Hour Review - A Mixed Bag! The Xbox Series X and S have just launched globally! In this video, I talk through my usage after a couple of days since the unboxing in a full in-depth, walkthrough review! All the features and my impressions of the Xbox Series X after some real everyday use. In terms of specs, it has an 8x Cores @ 3.8 GHz (3.66 GHz w/ SMT) Custom Zen 2 CPU and a 12 TFLOPS, 52 CUs @ 1.825 GHz Custom RDNA 2 GPU. 16 GB GDDR6 Memory, 10GB @ 560 GB/s, 6GB @ 336 GB/s. The Series X internal storage is a 1 TB Custom NVME SSD. You can play games in 4K at 120fps providing you have the appropriate gaming monitor / TV like the LG CX that I have in this video.  90hz refresh rate 6.76" OLED display, a 50MP Camera, and 4K video! The controller is almost identical to the Xbox One controller but there have been a few subtle changes which many will like. There are so many exclusive gaming titles for both Xbox Series X and the also new PS5, but which is the better console? Also is the Series X worth £200 more vs the Series S?

snippet.description:
Good things come in pairs.  

A Binding of Kin is the next Chapter in Dead by Daylight. The Twins - Charlotte and Victor Deshayes - formed an emotional bond like none other. After a life of hardship and suffering, The Entity has twisted their love for one another into something truly terrifying. The new Survivor is Élodie Rakoto. Cunning, smart, and resolute, Élodie spent her life trying to uncover the mystery of her parents’ disappearance. Grief-stricken and guilt-ridden, she turned to the occult to find the answers she was looking for. 

COMING SOON. 

Dead by Daylight is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror game where one player takes on the role of a brutal Killer and the other four play as Survivors. As a Killer, your goal is to sacrifice as many Survivors as possible. As a Survivor, your goal is to escape and avoid being caught and killed.

snippet.title: Apple's M1 Mac is not what you think...
snippet.description:
The first Apple Silicon Macs are here sporting the new M1 SoC. What does it mean for Macs today and into the future? Let's find out!
Sign up for Setapp today! https://setapp.com/?utm_source=snazzylabs&utm_campaign=apps&utm_medium=sponsorship

Check out my gear/suggestions! - http://amazon.com/shop/snazzylabs

Subscribe to my podcast Flashback! - http://relay.fm/flashback
Follow me on Twitter - http://twitter.com/snazzyq
Follow me on Instagram - http://instagram.com/snazzyq

At long last, Apple has finally announced and will soon be releasing Arm-based Macs based on Apple's new "Apple Silicon" family. This new chip, the M1, is based on the A14 and makes its way to the MacBook Air, 13" MacBook Pro with Touch Bar, and Mac mini. Specs are vague and performance is yet to be determined, but if Apple's slides are to be believed, this chip design and these machines are just the beginning of a hugely important transition for Apple and computing in general. But let's go beyond what Apple said in the keynote and dive into some of the nuance behind this new Apple Silicon M1 chip.

snippet.title: Brawl Stars: Brawl Talk! New Season, Ice Brawler, and more!
snippet.description:
Subscribe to our Brawl Stars Esports channel! https://www.youtube.com/brawlstarsesports

Download NOW!! ►► https://supr.cl/playbrawl
Be a BRAWLER! Subscribe! ►► https://supr.cl/subscribe

Fast-paced 3v3 multiplayer and battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES
- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

Features:
- Team up for real-time 3v3 battles against players from across the world
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile
- Unlock and collect new, powerful Brawlers - each with a signature attack and Super ability
- New events and game modes daily
- Battle solo or with friends
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings 
- Join or start your own Club with fellow players to share tips and battle together
- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins
- Player-designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master

From the makers of Clash of Clans, Clash Royale and Boom Beach!

Support:
Contact us in-game via Settings, Help and Support — or visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/brawl-stars/

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: Xbox Series X Unboxing & 48 Hour Review | A Mixed Bag!
snippet.description:
Xbox Series X Unboxing & 48 Hour Review - A Mixed Bag! The Xbox Series X and S have just launched globally! In this video, I talk through my usage after a couple of days since the unboxing in a full in-depth, walkthrough review! All the features and my impressions of the Xbox Series X after some real everyday use. In terms of specs, it has an 8x Cores @ 3.8 GHz (3.66 GHz w/ SMT) Custom Zen 2 CPU and a 12 TFLOPS, 52 CUs @ 1.825 GHz Custom RDNA 2 GPU. 16 GB GDDR6 Memory, 10GB @ 560 GB/s, 6GB @ 336 GB/s. The Series X internal storage is a 1 TB Custom NVME SSD. You can play games in 4K at 120fps providing you have the appropriate gaming monitor / TV like the LG CX that I have in this video.  90hz refresh rate 6.76" OLED display, a 50MP Camera, and 4K video! The controller is almost identical to the Xbox One controller but there have been a few subtle changes which many will like. There are so many exclusive gaming titles for both Xbox Series X and the also new PS5, but which is the better console? Also is the Series X worth £200 more vs the Series S?

snippet.title: The Stunning Transformation Of Susan Boyle
snippet.description:
After her star-making appearance on Britain's Got Talent, Susan Boyle secured a place in all of our hearts. But her path to fame wasn't an easy one. If you're curious about her early life and how she got to where she is today, keep watching to witness her stunning transformation.

Boyle was born in 1961 in Blackburn, Scotland to Patrick and Bridget Boyle, a miner and a typist, respectively. She was the youngest of nine siblings, and her mother was 47 when she gave birth to her.

Due to a difficult birth, Boyle experienced a lack of oxygen as an infant, resulting in a condition that at the time was thought to be mild brain damage. As a result, she grew up with some learning challenges and became the target of bullying in school. Despite her childhood hardships, she's characterized herself as a "cheeky little girl" who fought very hard to carve out a space of her own among her siblings.

With her mother's unwavering support, Boyle found her way to singing just before her teenage years. She discovered her iconic talent by participating in school productions and performing with her church choir. 

But for much of Boyle's early life, singing was merely an activity that she did for pleasure, not a skill that could lead to a career.

Keep watching this video to see Susan Boyle's stunning transformation.

snippet.title: Apple's M1 Mac is not what you think...
snippet.description:
The first Apple Silicon Macs are here sporting the new M1 SoC. What does it mean for Macs today and into the future? Let's find out!
Sign up for Setapp today! https://setapp.com/?utm_source=snazzylabs&utm_campaign=apps&utm_medium=sponsorship

Check out my gear/suggestions! - http://amazon.com/shop/snazzylabs

Subscribe to my podcast Flashback! - http://relay.fm/flashback
Follow me on Twitter - http://twitter.com/snazzyq
Follow me on Instagram - http://instagram.com/snazzyq

At long last, Apple has finally announced and will soon be releasing Arm-based Macs based on Apple's new "Apple Silicon" family. This new chip, the M1, is based on the A14 and makes its way to the MacBook Air, 13" MacBook Pro with Touch Bar, and Mac mini. Specs are vague and performance is yet to be determined, but if Apple's slides are to be believed, this chip design and these machines are just the beginning of a hugely important transition for Apple and computing in general. But let's go beyond what Apple said in the keynote and dive into some of the nuance behind this new Apple Silicon M1 chip.

snippet.title: Rapper Mo3 shot dead on Dallas highway
snippet.description:
DALLAS - Rapper Mo3 was shot dead on a Dallas highway on Wednesday, sources tell FOX4.

The rapper, whose real name was Melvin Noble, was killed midday in an incident on northbound Interstate 35 near Clarendon Drive.

Dallas police declined to publicly confirm the rapper, 28, was killed in the shooting, but did release a narrative of the incident.

Police said he was in a vehicle on I-35 just before noon when a suspect approached Mo3’s car.

Both men stopped their vehicles, the victim got out and started running but was shot several times on the highway.

A bystander inside another vehicle was struck as well. Police say that person did not suffer life threatening injuries.

Police are still looking for the shooter of the Dallas-based rapper.

Video circulating on social media purports to show Mo3 lying on the highway as someone tries to help him after being shot.

Mo3 had previously said that he was the victim of a non-fatal 2019 shooting.

Mo3’s most notable hit was "Errybody (Remix),” collaboration with Boosie Badazz. 

FOX 4 News is a FOX-owned station serving Dallas-Fort Worth and all of North Texas.

snippet.title: Why do Biden's votes not follow Benford's Law?
snippet.description:
My book is cheap at Waterstones and signed at Maths Gear:
https://www.waterstones.com/book/humble-pi/matt-parker/9780141989143
https://mathsgear.co.uk/products/humble-pi-signed-paperback

Check out Steve Mould's Numberphile video about Benford's Law.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XXjlR2OK1kM

Buy a signed copy of "How Many Socks Make a Pair?" by Rob Eastaway.
https://mathsgear.co.uk/products/copy-of-signed-copy-of-why-do-busses-come-in-threes

There’s more on Mark Nigrini’s work here:
http://www.nigrini.com/benfords-law/

"Benford's Law and the Detection of Election Fraud" 2011 paper.
https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/political-analysis/article/benfords-law-and-the-detection-of-election-fraud/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D

And for balance, here is a paper critical of that other paper (but only in the use of a 'second digit' check and they do not dispute the main Benford's Law claims.). https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/e667/b8ad9f58992828ff820ddc8a005de754c5f5.pdf
And here is a paper by the same author specifically about the 2020 US election results:
http://www-personal.umich.edu/~wmebane/inapB.pdf

Get your Chicago Board of Election Commissioners data here!
https://chicagoelections.gov/en/election-results.asp?election=251&race=11

Yep, 2069 precincts. Some would say that's too many.
https://data.cityofchicago.org/Facilities-Geographic-Boundaries/Precincts-current-/uvpq-qeeq

If you must, here are links to people using Benford's Law to suggest the Biden votes were fraudulent. Please do no harass or brigade anyone.
https://github.com/cjph8914/2020_benfords/blob/main/Chicago_Wards_Precincts_Benfords_Data.ipynb
https://jonsnewplace.wordpress.com/2020/11/07/joe-bidens-votes-violate-benfords-law-mathematics-gnews/

CORRECTIONS
- Hello loyal viewer. If you are reading this you most likely regularly watch my videos and know that I put corrections here. But the comment section on this video has been, to put it lightly, "wild". I don't think anyone is checking the corrections here! So I'm going to break with tradition and put the corrections in a pinned comment. But in short:
- I should have said I used the Chicago data (instead of a swing state, let's say) because that is what people claiming election fraud were using. I didn't pick it myself to make a point.
- Foolishly I cut a bit of the video where I talk about how Trump's data is also a bad Benford fit but that massive spike of 1s makes it look like a good match. Check out how low 3, 4 and 5 are.
- There has been specific criticism of aspects of that paper I read from, but only the usual back-and-forth of academics. Everyone agrees with the idea that Benford is not a magic tool to detect election fraud (nor is any statistical tool really; they all require careful interpretation).
- As always, let me know if you spot any other mistakes.

Thanks to my Patreon supporters who mean I can spend TWO DAYS trawling through election stats and making plots. I'm meant to be writing a new book you know. So, thanks a lot.

https://www.patreon.com/standupmaths

As always: thanks to Jane Street who support my channel. They're amazing.
https://www.janestreet.com/

Filming and editing by Matt Parker
Music by Howard Carter
Design by Simon Wright and Adam Robinson

MATT PARKER: Stand-up Mathematician

https://www.waterstones.com/book/humble-pi/matt-parker/9780141989143
https://mathsgear.co.uk/products/humble-pi-signed-paperback

Check out Steve Mould's Numberphile video about Benford's Law.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XXjlR2OK1kM

Buy a signed copy of "How Many Socks Make a Pair?" by Rob Eastaway.
https://mathsgear.co.uk/products/copy-of-signed-copy-of-why-do-busses-come-in-threes

There’s more on Mark Nigrini’s work here:
http://www.nigrini.com/benfords-law/

"Benford's Law and the Detection of Election Fraud" 2011 paper.
https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/political-analysis/article/benfords-law-and-the-detection-of-election-fraud/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D

And for balance, here is a paper critical of that other paper (but only in the use of a 'second digit' check and they do not dispute the main Benford's Law claims.). https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/e667/b8ad9f58992828ff820ddc8a005de754c5f5.pdf
And here is a paper by the same author specifically about the 2020 US election results:
http://www-personal.umich.edu/~wmebane/inapB.pdf

Get your Chicago Board of Election Commissioners data here!
https://chicagoelections.gov/en/election-results.asp?election=251&race=11

Yep, 2069 precincts. Some would say that's too many.
https://data.cityofchicago.org/Facilities-Geographic-Boundaries/Precincts-current-/uvpq-qeeq

If you must, here are links to people using Benford's Law to suggest the Biden votes were fraudulent. Please do no harass or brigade anyone.
https://github.com/cjph8914/2020_benfords/blob/main/Chicago_Wards_Precincts_Benfords_Data.ipynb
https://jonsnewplace.wordpress.com/2020/11/07/joe-bidens-votes-violate-benfords-law-mathematics-gnews/

CORRECTIONS
- Hello loyal viewer. If you are reading this you most likely regularly watch my videos and know that I put corrections here. But the comment section on this video has been, to put it lightly, "wild". I don't think anyone is checking the corrections here! So I'm going to break with tradition and put the corrections in a pinned comment. But in short:
- I should have said I used the Chicago data (instead of a swing state, let's say) because that is what people claiming election fraud were using. I didn't pick it myself to make a point.
- Foolishly I cut a bit of the video where I talk about how Trump's data is also a bad Benford fit but that massive spike of 1s makes it look like a good match. Check out how low 3, 4 and 5 are.
- There has been specific criticism of aspects of that paper I read from, but only the usual back-and-forth of academics. Everyone agrees with the idea that Benford is not a magic tool to detect election fraud (nor is any statistical tool really; they all require careful interpretation).
- As always, let me know if you spot any other mistakes.

Thanks to my Patreon supporters who mean I can spend TWO DAYS trawling through election stats and making plots. I'm meant to be writing a new book you know. So, thanks a lot.

https://www.patreon.com/standupmaths

As always: thanks to Jane Street who support my channel. They're amazing.
https://www.janestreet.com/

Filming and editing by Matt Parker
Music by Howard Carter
Design by Simon Wright and Adam Robinson

snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | A Binding of Kin | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Good things come in pairs.  

A Binding of Kin is the next Chapter in Dead by Daylight. The Twins - Charlotte and Victor Deshayes - formed an emotional bond like none other. After a life of hardship and suffering, The Entity has twisted their love for one another into something truly terrifying. The new Survivor is Élodie Rakoto. Cunning, smart, and resolute, Élodie spent her life trying to uncover the mystery of her parents’ disappearance. Grief-stricken and guilt-ridden, she turned to the occult to find the answers she was looking for. 

COMING SOON. 

Dead by Daylight is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror game where one player takes on the role of a brutal Killer and the other four play as Survivors. As a Killer, your goal is to sacrifice as many Survivors as possible. As a Survivor, your goal is to escape and avoid being caught and killed.

After a life of hardship and suffering, The Entity has twisted their love for one another into something truly terrifying. The new Survivor is Élodie Rakoto. Cunning, smart, and resolute, Élodie spent her life trying to uncover the mystery of her parents’ disappearance. Grief-stricken and guilt-ridden, she turned to the occult to find the answers she was looking for. 

COMING SOON.

snippet.title: FA Chairman Greg Clarke apologises for use of 'coloured players' during committee hearing
snippet.description:
The FA chairman, Greg Clarke, was made to apologise during a select committee hearing after using the term 'coloured footballers'. Clarke was addressing MPs about the current crisis of funding and governance within football. Clarke said: 'If I look at what happens to high-profile female footballers, high-profile coloured footballers and the abuse they take on social media … they take absolutely terrible abuse'. Clarke was later asked to retract his remarks by the committee member Kevin Brennan and did so, saying: 'If I said it I deeply apologise for it.'

President-elect Biden and Vice President-elect Kamala Harris are delivering remarks in Wilmington, Delaware, after their projected victory at 8 p.m. ET.

#JoeBiden #2020Election #PresidentialElection

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Aston Villa (0-3) | Premier League
snippet.description:
We were well-beaten by Aston Villa on a deeply disappointing night at Emirates Stadium on Sunday.
 
Coming into the game on the back of a morale-boosting win at Old Trafford, hopes were high but the visitors immediately underlined their attacking intent when, just seconds into the match, John McGinn swept the ball into the top corner.
 
Villa celebrated wildly, but the decision was checked by VAR – and the ‘goal’ ruled out as Ross Barkley was offside and adjudged to be impeding the view of Bernd Leno as McGinn struck the ball.
 
It was a major let-off for us, but we struggled to impose ourselves for much of the first half – although Willian blazed one effort over the bar after good work by Thomas Partey and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.
 
But it was the visitors who took the lead when Matt Targett swept the ball across the face of goal and it was bundled in off the unfortunate Bukayo Saka.
 
We responded positively and had a golden chance to equalise when Kieran Tierney’s pinpoint cross from the left picked out Alex Lacazette, but the forward could not keep his header down.
 
It was a disappointing end to a disappointing half, but after the restart it was the visitors who were first to threaten again, with Bernd Leno forced to palm away Trezeguet’s shot.
 
Jack Grealish then came close to extending Villa’s advantage from close range, only to see his curling effort deflected behind - before Rob Holding fired wide at the other end.
 
Nicolas Pepe and Eddie Nketiah were soon thrown into the fray as we looked for a way back into the game, with the former coming close with a fine curling effort.
 
But Villa’s fluent attacking display was rewarded with a second goal when Douglas Luiz found Barkley at the back post, and his volleyed cross was headed in by Ollie Watkins.
 
The Villa striker then made it three moments later to compound a miserable night for us at Emirates Stadium.
 
#arsenal #premierleague 

Enjoy match highlights, training and behind the scenes to get closer to the likes of Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang, David Luiz, Vivianne Miedema, Nicolas Pepe, Alexandre Lacazette, Leah Williamson, Mesut Ozil, Bernd Leno, Danielle van de Donk, Willian, Hector Bellerin, Jordan Nobbs, Bukayo Saka, Kim Little, Gabriel Martinelli, Thomas Partey and more.

snippet.title: Can Trump steal the election?
snippet.description:
Republican lawsuits in the 2020 Election don’t amount to much. But the future of election law under a new US Supreme Court is a different story. 
 
Become a Video Lab member! http://bit.ly/video-lab
 
When Joe Biden won the US Presidential election, President Donald Trump threatened legal action in some of the battleground states that were among the last to count their ballots. It was all part of a campaign to cast doubt on the legality of mail-in ballots, which disproportionately favored Joe Biden. The lawsuits themselves likely won’t alter the course of the election. But one in Pennsylvania sheds light on how the current US Supreme Court might rule on future election laws.

snippet.description:
Joe Biden is on the verge of becoming the next president of the United States. 

The counting continues in a handful of remaining battleground states.  But Joe Biden has now overtaken Donald Trump in key states including Pennsylvania,  where 98% of the votes have been counted. 

Victory in Pennsylvania alone, with its 20 electoral college votes, would be enough to deliver Joe Biden the White House. 

Sophie Raworth presents BBC News at Ten reporting by North America editor Jon Sopel and Nick Bryant with the Biden campaign in Delaware.

snippet.title: 芋头的一生，辣椒…是送的The life of taro…and pepper is today’s treat丨Liziqi Channel
snippet.description:
Please  subscribe to 【李子柒 Liziqi 】Liziqi Channel on YouTube if you like my videos: https://goo.gl/nkjpSx
 #李子柒#Liziqi#ChineseCuisine #ChineseFood

小时候我爷爷教过一句让我很疑惑的顺口溜：“红薯芋头本姓张，煮的没有烧的香”…虽然到现在也想不明白为啥一定要姓“张”但一点也不妨碍我爱吃它！年初在前院大门口种了几排毛芋儿后门那多种了香芋，刚好也到了能下嘴的季节。芋儿鸡、烤芋儿、红糖芋圆蛋…你们呢？最喜欢怎么吃芋头啊？
When I was little, grandpa taught me a rather puzzling jingle: “Sweet potato and taro are surnamed Zhang, better roasted than boiled for long.” Even today I still haven’t figured out why on earth they had anything to do with the surname Zhang, but I love them anyway! At the beginning of the year, several rows of taro were planted at the gate of the front yard, and water yam at the back door. Now it’s just the time to feast on them. Taro with chicken stew, roasted taro, eggs with taro balls in brown sugar…And you? How do you like your taro best?

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Man Utd vs Arsenal (0-1) | Aubameyang penalty earns victory at Old Trafford
snippet.description:
A second-half penalty from captain Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang gave us a richly-deserved three points at Old Trafford - our first Premier League win there for 14 years.

We were the more positive side right from the opening exchanges, snapping into tackles and closing down well, and much of the opening quarter of an hour was played in the United half.

Our first sight of goal came when the overlapping Hector Bellerin fizzed a low ball across goal, but it was just ahead of the sliding Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang at the far post.

Despite our superiority in terms of possession, it was United who had the first shot on target when Mason Greenwood ghosted in at the far post to draw a smart low save from Bernd Leno.

We kept driving forward. Alexandre Lacazette had the ball nicked off his toes inside the area when he was about to pull the trigger while Willian fired against the bar after a neat one two with Aubameyang.

But the best chance of the half came late on. Bukayo Saka then headed over from a glorious position in front of goal, set up by Bellerin's pinpoint cross.

Aubameyang sent a shot just wide at the start of the second half before Thomas Partey brought a save from David De Gea with a fierce drive.

We certainly deserved the lead when it came. We had been knocking at the door and finally went ahead from the penalty spot. Bellerin was brought down in the area by Paul Pogba and Aubameyang strode up to tuck home from 12 yards and end a personal five-game scoreless run in the Premier League.

We came under much more pressure in the final ten minutes and United hit the post late on when a Donny van de Beek shot cannoned off Mohamed Elneny and then the upright.

But hang on we did, to record our first Premier League win at Old Trafford since 2006.

snippet.title: The Electoral College, explained
snippet.description:
Why some Americans’ votes count more than others.

Watch more of our election coverage: http://vox.com/ElectionVideos

In the 2000 US presidential election, the Democratic candidate got half a million more votes than the Republican. The Democrat lost. Sixteen years later the same thing happened again. In the US, if you run for president, it does not actually matter how many people in the country vote for you. What matters instead is an arcane system for selecting America’s head of state called the Electoral College.

The Electoral College is the reason the US has something called “swing states,” and it’s the reason those places get to decide the future of the country. It’s the reason presidential candidates almost never campaign in the country’s biggest cities. And more recently, it’s also the reason that Republican candidates have been able to eke out victories in the presidential election without actually getting the most votes.

The Electoral College makes some Americans’ votes more powerful than others. In fact, that’s part of the reason we have it to begin with; in the country’s early years, the Electoral College helped give the votes of Southern Whites more weight than the votes of Northerners. The idea at its core, that certain votes simply matter more than others, is baked into the American tradition. In the 2020 election, it may decide the winner.

Further reading:
The historian Alexander Keyssar’s book “Why Do We Still Have the Electoral College?” takes you through the history and function of the Electoral College: https://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674660151

For the bite-sized version of that history, Keyssar also wrote this piece in the New York Times: https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/03/opinion/electoral-college-racism-white-supremacy.html

The Times also had a great interactive feature on where the 2020 candidates actually spent money: https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/10/17/us/politics/trump-biden-campaign-ad-spending.html

Pew has a breakdown of how democracies around the world elect their head of state, which really shows what an oddball the US is: https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2016/11/22/among-democracies-u-s-stands-out-in-how-it-chooses-its-head-of-state/

More on why today’s Electoral College gives Republican presidential candidates a structural advantage: https://www.vox.com/policy-and-politics/2019/9/17/20868790/republicans-lose-popular-vote-win-electoral-college

snippet.title: TWICE 「BETTER」 Music Video
snippet.description:
TWICE JAPAN 7th SINGLE『BETTER』  
2020.11.18 Release! 

【いい音楽で一度、素晴らしいパフォーマンスで二度魅了させる】と言う意味を持つ、Asia No.1最強ガールズグループTWICE。

2020年11月18日（水）にJAPAN 7th SINGLE『BETTER』（読み：ベター）をリリース。

普段人がいるはずの場所などに一人ぼっちでいる彼女たちが、そこから自力で抜け出して、みんなが一つでいられる世界に向かうなど、現代を反映したイメージと歌詞に合わせた世界観を表している。
また今回は、「いつも一緒」という思いを込めた、9人一体のパフォーマンスも見どころ。

Photos by Jung Minhee (Project Mu studio), JJeary

The 20 electoral votes Biden won in Pennsylvania allowed him to surpass the 270 needed to win the election, according to projections by the Associated Press. He has received 284 electoral votes to Republican President Donald Trump's  214.

snippet.title: What Joe Biden won – and what he didn't
snippet.description:
Biden beat Trump. Now what? Ezra Klein explains.

Watch more of our election coverage: http://vox.com/ElectionVideos

The 2020 US election is over, and former vice president Joe Biden will be the 46th US president. He’s the first to defeat an incumbent president in 28 years, and he did it in part by unifying the Democratic Party against Donald Trump, bringing members of the party’s left wing into his campaign after beating Bernie Sanders in the primary, and crafting an aggressive policy platform.

But Biden’s agenda will most likely be met by a Republican-controlled Senate, whose leader, Mitch McConnell, presided over the complete stonewalling of the last Democratic president’s agenda, and likely intends to do so again. This despite the fact that many of Biden’s policies enjoy the support of most Americans, and McConnell’s Senate caucus represents a minority of them.

In other words, Biden’s decisive victory margin of several million votes was basically good enough for a stalemate. In this video, Vox editor-at-large Ezra Klein explains what makes that possible -- a Republican Party dedicated to making sure a minority controls the country -- and how Joe Biden’s first priority should be unwinding that system back to democracy.

Read more about the Biden presidency from Vox:
Ezra Klein on how Biden won: https://www.vox.com/21545969/joe-biden-2020-election-winner-trump-vote

Dylan Matthews on what a President Biden will be up against: https://www.vox.com/2020/11/6/21534594/joe-biden-wins-2020-presidential-election

Ian Millhiser on who the US Senate actually represents: https://www.vox.com/2020/11/6/21550979/senate-malapportionment-20-million-democrats-republicans-supreme-court

snippet.title: 'Don't be ridiculous': Rudy Giuliani learns about Biden win from reporters
snippet.description:
Rudy Giuliani, Donald Trump's personal attorney, was holding a press conference baselessly disputing the legitimacy of the US presidential election when news filtered through that Joe Biden had been declared the winner. 

Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

'Who was it called by?' Giuliani asked, referring to the broadcast news networks. 'All of them,' replied a reporter. The former New York City mayor insisted the result could not be called until the Trump campaign's legal challenges had gone to court.

The press conference had been called outside Four Seasons Total Landscaping, a suburban business situated between a crematorium and an adult book store on the outskirts of Philadelphia. It was unclear whether the campaign had mistaken it for the noted hotel of the same name.

The race for the White House has narrowed to hinge on a handful of crucial battleground states that remain too close to call. President Trump exceeded expectations and captured several large swing states that Joe Biden had hoped would solidify his path to victory, but millions of early votes remain outstanding. Watch CBSN's continuing coverage for live election results and analysis.

snippet.title: Can Trump steal the election?
snippet.description:
Republican lawsuits in the 2020 Election don’t amount to much. But the future of election law under a new US Supreme Court is a different story. 
 
Become a Video Lab member! http://bit.ly/video-lab
 
When Joe Biden won the US Presidential election, President Donald Trump threatened legal action in some of the battleground states that were among the last to count their ballots. It was all part of a campaign to cast doubt on the legality of mail-in ballots, which disproportionately favored Joe Biden. The lawsuits themselves likely won’t alter the course of the election. But one in Pennsylvania sheds light on how the current US Supreme Court might rule on future election laws.

snippet.title: I Let The Instagram Shop Tab Pick My Outfits
snippet.description:
You can download Honey for FREE today! ▸ http://joinhoney.com/safiya 
Honey finds coupons with the click of a button. A big thank you to Honey for sponsoring today's video!

Hello friends! Today, I return to the land of internet hauls and social media targeted recommendations - with a deep dive into the Instagram shop tab! Previously, I have bought things recommended to me via targeted ads on Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, and Snapchat - and when the shop tab was rolled out - peeking its lil head out from behind the explore page - I was instantly intrigued. snippet.title: How Large Can a Bacteria get? Life & Size 3
snippet.description:
The first 1000 people to use this link will get a free trial of Skillshare: 
https://skl.sh/kurzgesagt9

https://shop.kurzgesagt.org/

Sources & further reading:

In and out, in and out. Staying alive is about doing things. This very second, your cells are combusting glucose molecules with oxygen to make energy available, which keeps you alive for another precious moment. To get the oxygen to your cells you are breathing.
Breathing is an answer to a very hard problem: How do you get the resources that your cells need to survive, from the outside, to the inside of your cells? Every living thing has to solve this problem and the solution is surprisingly different depending on one of the most important regulators of life: Size.

snippet.title: Survivors of White Island Disaster say they felt abandoned after eruption | 60 Minutes Australia
snippet.description:
Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | White Island Volcano Disaster (2020)

It’s a terrible truth to have to acknowledge. The White Island volcano in New Zealand is not only spectacular but spectacularly dangerous. One awful afternoon last December, it erupted, seemingly without warning. Forty-seven tourists and guides, who up until the catastrophic explosion had only been thinking of adventure, were stranded on the island. All suffered injuries, and 21 died. Now, for the first time, Australian survivors talk about that tragic day and its devastating aftermath. They tell Sarah Abo it is a miracle that more people weren’t killed. But they also express their anger and ask questions about why they were allowed to visit such a perilous location in the first place, and why efforts to rescue them were flawed.

snippet.title: WATCH: Election results for Trump, Biden and key swing state races | USA TODAY
snippet.description:
Results from the 2020 presidential election as Americans vote in races for the presidency, 11 governorships, 35 Senate seats and all 435 House seats.

Final polls show the race between President Donald Trump and Democratic nominee Joe Biden has tightened since mid-October, both nationally and in battleground states.

Biden's lead in USA TODAY's average of averages, which is based on data from RealClearPolitics and FiveThirtyEight, reached double-digits on Oct. 12, but has since fallen back to a 7.5-percentage point lead. That leaves him back roughly in the same position USA TODAY found him in its first poll roundup on Sept. 28, when his polling average lead over Trump was 7.2 points. 

Beyond the presidency, Tuesday's election may result in changes in Congress, where Democrats want to regain control of the Republican-led Senate and Democrats hope to expand their advantage in the House.

» Watch more on this and other topics from USA TODAY: https://bit.ly/30HuLzS

O time rubro negro foi goleado duas vezes seguidas no brasileirão, sofreu 4x1 pro São Paulo do dinizismo e agora levou 4x0 do Galo doido do Sampaoli. O que tá acontecendo com o mengão? Que doideira!

O Abel Braga catalão
Provou que tem talento
Talento em ser humilhado
Nisso o cara é gênio

Ebola no gol toda hora
Mano, até a filha da Xuxa
Bate no Flamengo
Foi 4 Ilarilariê 
Com chumbo e tudo dentro

Chama o SAMU que o Mengo tá fraco
E também acuda
O Poze que já tá à beira de um infarto

Zaga-peneira é a nova moda
Mano Dome acho que adora
O ato de levar bola nas costas

Já levou um baile lindo do Dragão
E cinco do Del Valle na sua testa
Botaram uma Ferrari pra quem
Aguenta pilotar somente um Celta


A fase do Mengão tá difícil demais
Olha o Flamengo, vei...

No Among Us é gênio

No time do Flamengo

Ebola no gol toda hora
O GabiTrump ergueu a placa 
Só que escrito dentro
Estava "Pare a contagem"
Quanto sofrimento!

Até o Lisca sabe 
Qual é o vício do Flamengo
E levar quatro do Galão
É vício já faz tempo

Mais uma surra, agora do Galo
Quem é que cura?
O novo viciado em levar de quatro?

O Corona abriu a porta
Pra chegar o vírus da Ebola

Gerou primeiro um couro Dinizista
E, em BH, um couro careca

A fase do Mengão tá difícil demais

Ebola no gol toda hora
O Abel Braga catalão
Provou que tem talento
Talento em ser humilhado
Nisso o cara é gênio

Ebola no gol toda hora
Mano, até a filha da Xuxa
Bate no Flamengo
Foi 4 Ilarilariê 
Com chumbo e tudo dentro

Chama o SAMU que o Mengo tá fraco
E também acuda
O Poze que já tá à beira de um infarto

Zaga-peneira é a nova moda
Mano Dome acho que adora
O ato de levar bola nas costas

Já levou um baile lindo do Dragão
E cinco do Del Valle na sua testa
Botaram uma Ferrari pra quem
Aguenta pilotar somente um Celta


A fase do Mengão tá difícil demais
Olha o Flamengo, vei...

Ebola no gol toda hora

No Among Us é gênio
Tá dando aula de impostor
No time do Flamengo

Ebola no gol toda hora
O GabiTrump ergueu a placa 
Só que escrito dentro
Estava "Pare a contagem"
Quanto sofrimento!

Até o Lisca sabe 
Qual é o vício do Flamengo
E levar quatro do Galão
É vício já faz tempo

snippet.title: 5G und Corona – haben wir etwas übersehen? | Harald Lesch
snippet.description:
Die neue Mobilfunktechnik 5G soll die Corona-Pandemie ausgelöst haben – so liest man außerhalb der Mainstream-Medien und auf Facebook und Co. Radikale 5G-Gegner haben in Großbritannien, Belgien, Frankreich und Deutschland sogar schon Anschläge auf Mobilfunkmasten durchgeführt. Welche Argumente führen die Befürworter dieser Theorie ins Feld? Und wie ist das wissenschaftlich zu betrachten?

Dieses Video ist eine Produktion des ZDF, in Zusammenarbeit mit objektiv media.

snippet.title: Dein neues Hausrezept mit Gelinggarantie
snippet.description:
Heute geht es um Brot backen mit 3 Tassen Mehl, einfacher geht es nun wirklich nicht. Brot backen einfach und schnell, das ist ja da Motto auf meinem Kanal, denn jeder fängt man mit Brot backen an. 

Friss dich Dumm Brot: https://youtu.be/HffpdsJT8Kw

Im Video benutze Produkte: 

Brotmesser            https://amzn.to/31LK2k7 *
Tasse                           https://amzn.to/3elGPN7 *
Glasschüssel 26cm     https://amzn.to/3hNIVWO *
Glasschüssel 6cm    https://amzn.to/3hNPRTJ * 
Handmixer https://amzn.to/3m2Wvbb *
Backmatte            https://amzn.to/3gP0xQN *
Teigkarte https://amzn.to/3jCNeou * 
Kuchengitter            https://amzn.to/34QnoZM *
Mehlstreuer Edelstahl    https://amzn.to/3hLDkQI *
Mehlstreuer Kunststoff    https://amzn.to/3lDo3E0 *
Rasierklinge     https://amzn.to/2HNAEW3 *
Holzschneidebrett     https://amzn.to/2QGwjEO *

Zutaten: 
1 Tasse Weizenmehl Typ 550
2 Tassen Dinkelmehl Typ 630 
1-2 TL Trockenhefe
2 TL Salz
1,5 Tassen heißes Wasser

Zubereitung: 
Alle Zutaten in eine  große Schüssel geben und mit dem Handmixer verkneten. Auf die Konsistenz achten. Der Teig sollte sich von der Schüssel gut lösen. Im Zweifel den Teig lieber etwas fester lassen. Mit Frischhaltefolie abdecken und mindestens 3 Stunden in den Kühlschrank stellen. 
Nach der Gehzeit den Teig auf einer Backmatte falten und zu einer schönen Kugel formen. 
Die Kugel auf ein Backpapier legen und in einen Bräter (24cm) geben. Mit Mehl bestreuen, anschließend mit einer Rasierklinge ein schönes Muster in den Teig schneiden. 
Den Bräter mit Deckel in den Ofen stellen und  30 Minuten, Ober- und Unterhitze bei 200°C vorheizen. Nach den 30 Minuten den Deckel entfernen und weitere 30 Minuten bis zur gewünschten Bräune backen. Brot aus dem Ofen holen, auf einem Kuchengitter auskühlen lassen und genießen.

localizations.en-GB.title: Why this cheesecake is better than any other! [RECIPE]
localizations.en-GB.description:
This cheesecake recipe is a cross between a Japanese and a Spanish cheese cake. I once felt like trying something new and this cheesecake was made from it. Juicy without end and fluffy like the Japanese.

already subscribed for free? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Channel Support: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Handicraft second channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

The mug from the video: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Baking release spray: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (take the cheapest, everything is the same anyway ^^)
Men mixer: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Bosch Mixer: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredients:

600 gr. Cream cheese
400 gr. Cream
200 grams of sugar
4 eggs size M
2 tbsp flour type 405
1 teaspoon vanilla paste (or 1 x vanilla sugar)
1 pinch of salt


Preparation:

Separate the eggs and beat the egg white with a little sugar (20-30 gr.) Until stiff
Mix the egg yolks with the remaining ingredients until creamy
Now carefully fold in the egg whites
Put everything in a mold (line with wet baking paper and use aluminum foil at the bottom)
Put 1 liter of water on a baking sheet and heat the oven to 140 °
Put the cake in the oven and bake at 140 ° for 1 hour
Then increase the temperature to 175 ° for 10-20 minutes
Switch off the oven and open the oven door a crack (towel / wooden spoon)
Let the cake cool down slowly for about 10-15 minutes
Then take it out and let it cool down completely

localizations.ko.description:
이 치즈 케이크 레시피는 일본과 스페인 치즈 케이크의 교차점입니다. 나는 한때 새로운 것을 시도하고 싶었고이 치즈 케이크는 그것으로 만들어졌습니다. 끝없는 육즙과 일본인처럼 푹신 푹신.

이미 무료로 구독 하셨나요? 👍 : https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
채널 지원 : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
수공예 두 번째 채널 : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

비디오의 머그 : https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
베이킹 릴리스 스프레이 : https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (가장 저렴한 것을 가져 가십시오.
남자 믹서 : https://amzn.to/35izpag
보쉬 믹서 : https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

성분 :

600 gr. 크림 치즈
400 gr. 크림
설탕 200g
계란 4 개 M
밀가루 2 큰술 405 형
바닐라 페이스트 1 작은 술 (또는 바닐라 설탕 1 개)
소금 1 꼬집


예비:

계란을 분리하고 약간의 설탕 (20-30 gr.)으로 계란 흰자를 뻣뻣해질 때까지 치십시오
계란 노른자와 남은 재료를 크림이 될 때까지 섞습니다.
이제 달걀 흰자위를 조심스럽게 접 으세요
모든 것을 형태로 넣으십시오 (젖은 베이킹 페이퍼로 선을 긋고 바닥에 알루미늄 호일을 사용하십시오)
베이킹 시트에 물 1 리터를 넣고 오븐을 140 °로 가열합니다.
케이크를 오븐에 넣고 140 °에서 1 시간 동안 굽습니다.
그런 다음 온도를 10-20 분 동안 175 °로 높입니다.
오븐을 끄고 오븐 문에 금이 가세요 (수건 / 나무 숟가락)
케이크를 약 10-15 분 동안 천천히 식 힙니다.
그런 다음 꺼내서 완전히 식히십시오

localizations.hi.title: यह चीज़केक किसी भी अन्य से बेहतर क्यों है! [विधि]
localizations.hi.description:
यह चीज़केक नुस्खा एक जापानी और एक स्पेनिश पनीर केक के बीच एक क्रॉस है। मुझे एक बार ऐसा लगा कि मैं कुछ नया करने की कोशिश कर रहा हूं और यह चीज़केक इसी से बनाया गया है। जापानी बिना अंत और रसदार के बिना रसदार।

पहले से ही मुफ्त में सदस्यता ली है? Iny: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
चैनल का समर्थन: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYw/poin
हस्तकला दूसरा चैनल: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-Jwxw

वीडियो से मग: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
बेकिंग रिलीज़ स्प्रे: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (सबसे सस्ता लें, सब कुछ वैसे भी है ^ ^)
मेन मिक्सर: https://amzn.to/35izpag
बॉश मिक्सर: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

सामग्री:

600 जीआर। क्रीम पनीर
400 जीआर क्रीम
200 ग्राम चीनी
4 अंडे का आकार एम
2 tbsp आटा प्रकार 405
1 चम्मच वेनिला पेस्ट (या 1 एक्स वेनिला चीनी)
1 चुटकी नमक


तैयारी:

अंडों को अलग करें और अंडे की सफेदी को थोड़ी चीनी (20-30 जीआर) के साथ सख्त होने तक पीटें
मलाई होने तक बाकी सामग्री के साथ अंडे की जर्दी मिलाएं
अब सावधानी से अंडे की सफेदी को फोल्ड करें
एक सांचे में सब कुछ डालें (गीले बेकिंग पेपर के साथ पंक्ति और तल पर एल्यूमीनियम पन्नी का उपयोग करें)
एक बेकिंग शीट पर 1 लीटर पानी डालें और ओवन को 140 ° तक गर्म करें
केक को ओवन में डालें और 1 घंटे के लिए 140 ° पर बेक करें
फिर 10-20 मिनट के लिए तापमान को 175 ° तक बढ़ा दें
ओवन को बंद करें और ओवन के दरवाजे को एक दरार (तौलिया / लकड़ी के चम्मच) से खोलें
केक को लगभग 10-15 मिनट तक धीरे-धीरे ठंडा होने दें
फिर इसे बाहर निकालें और इसे पूरी तरह से ठंडा होने दें

localizations.en-US.title: Why this cheesecake is better than any other! [RECIPE]
localizations.en-US.description:
This cheesecake recipe is a cross between a Japanese and a Spanish cheese cake. I once felt like trying something new and this cheesecake was made from it. Juicy without end and fluffy like the Japanese.

already subscribed for free? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Channel Support: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join

The mug from the video: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Baking release spray: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (take the cheapest, everything is the same anyway ^^)
Men mixer: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Bosch Mixer: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredients:

600 gr. Cream cheese
400 gr. Cream
200 grams of sugar
4 eggs size M
2 tbsp flour type 405
1 teaspoon vanilla paste (or 1 x vanilla sugar)
1 pinch of salt


Preparation:

Separate the eggs and beat the egg white with a little sugar (20-30 gr.) Until stiff
Mix the egg yolks with the remaining ingredients until creamy
Now carefully fold in the egg whites
Put everything in a mold (line with wet baking paper and use aluminum foil at the bottom)
Put 1 liter of water on a baking sheet and heat the oven to 140 °
Put the cake in the oven and bake at 140 ° for 1 hour
Then increase the temperature to 175 ° for 10-20 minutes
Switch off the oven and open the oven door a crack (towel / wooden spoon)
Let the cake cool down slowly for about 10-15 minutes
Then take it out and let it cool down completely

localizations.zh-CN.description:
這種芝士蛋糕配方是日本芝士蛋糕和西班牙芝士蛋糕之間的交叉。我曾經想嘗試一些新的東西，而這個芝士蛋糕是用它做的。多汁無止境，蓬鬆如日。

配料：

600克奶油芝士
400克奶油
200克糖
4個雞蛋大小M
2湯匙405型麵粉
1茶匙香草醬（或1 x香草糖）
1撮鹽


製備：

分離雞蛋，並用少許糖（20-30克）打碎蛋白。
將蛋黃與剩餘成分混合至奶油狀
現在小心地將蛋清折疊
將所有物品放入模具中（與濕烘焙紙對齊，並在底部使用鋁箔）

localizations.pt.description:
Esta receita de cheesecake é um cruzamento entre um bolo de queijo japonês e um espanhol. Uma vez tive vontade de experimentar algo novo e este cheesecake foi feito com isso. Suculento sem fim e fofo como o japonês.

já se inscreveu gratuitamente? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Suporte de canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Segundo canal de artesanato: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

A caneca do vídeo: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray de liberação de cozimento: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (pegue o mais barato, tudo é igual de qualquer maneira ^^)
Misturador masculino: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mixer Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredientes:

600 gr de cream cheese
400 gr. Creme
200 gramas de açucar
4 ovos tamanho M
2 colheres de sopa de farinha tipo 405
1 colher de chá de pasta de baunilha (ou 1 x açúcar de baunilha)
1 pitada de sal


Preparação:

Separe os ovos e bata as claras com um pouco de açúcar (20-30 gr.) Até ficarem firmes
Misture as gemas com os ingredientes restantes até ficar cremoso
Agora, envolva cuidadosamente as claras em neve
Coloque tudo em uma forma (forre com papel manteiga e use papel alumínio no fundo)
Coloque 1 litro de água em uma assadeira e aqueça o forno a 140 °
Coloque o bolo no forno e leve ao forno a 140 ° por 1 hora
Em seguida, aumente a temperatura para 175 ° por 10-20 minutos
Desligue o forno e abra a porta do forno uma fresta (toalha / colher de pau)
Deixe o bolo esfriar lentamente por cerca de 10-15 minutos
Em seguida, retire e deixe esfriar completamente

Ingrediënten:

600 gr Roomkaas
400 gr Room
200 gram suiker
4 eieren maat M
2 el bloem type 405
1 theelepel vanillepasta (of 1 x vanillesuiker)
1 snufje zout


Voorbereiding:

Scheid de eieren en klop de eiwitten met een beetje suiker (20-30 gr.) Stijf
Meng de eidooiers met de overige ingrediënten tot een romig geheel
Spatel nu voorzichtig het eiwit erdoor
Doe alles in een vorm (lijn met nat bakpapier en gebruik aluminiumfolie aan de onderkant)

Verhoog vervolgens de temperatuur tot 175 ° gedurende 10-20 minuten
Schakel de oven uit en open de ovendeur een kier (handdoek / houten lepel)
Laat de cake ongeveer 10-15 minuten langzaam afkoelen
Haal het er dan uit en laat het volledig afkoelen

localizations.fr.title: Pourquoi ce cheesecake est meilleur que tout autre! [RECETTE]
localizations.fr.description:
Cette recette de cheesecake est un croisement entre un gâteau au fromage japonais et espagnol. Une fois, j'ai eu envie d'essayer quelque chose de nouveau et ce cheesecake en était fait. Juteux sans fin et moelleux comme les japonais.

déjà abonné gratuitement? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Prise en charge de la chaîne: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Artisanat deuxième canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

Le mug de la vidéo: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray anti-cuisson: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (prenez le moins cher, tout est pareil quand même ^^)
Mixeur hommes: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mélangeur Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingrédients:

600 gr. De fromage à la crème
400 gr de crème
200 grammes de sucre
4 œufs taille M
2 cuillères à soupe de farine type 405
1 cuillère à café de pâte de vanille (ou 1 x sucre vanillé)
1 pincée de sel


Préparation:

Séparez les œufs et battez les blancs d'œufs avec un peu de sucre (20-30 gr.) Jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient fermes
Mélanger les jaunes d'œufs avec le reste des ingrédients jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient crémeux
Maintenant, incorporer soigneusement les blancs d'œufs
Mettez le tout dans une forme (ligne avec du papier sulfurisé humide et utilisez une feuille d'aluminium en bas)
Mettre 1 litre d'eau sur une plaque à pâtisserie et chauffer le four à 140 °
Mettre le gâteau au four et cuire à 140 ° pendant 1 heure
Ensuite, augmentez la température à 175 ° pendant 10-20 minutes
Éteignez le four et ouvrez la porte du four une fissure (serviette / cuillère en bois)
Laissez le gâteau refroidir lentement pendant environ 10 à 15 minutes
Ensuite, retirez-le et laissez-le refroidir complètement

4 huevos talla M
2 cucharadas de harina tipo 405
1 cucharadita de pasta de vainilla (o 1 x azúcar de vainilla)
1 pizca de sal


Preparación:

Separar los huevos y batir la clara con un poco de azúcar (20-30 gr.) Hasta que quede rígida
Mezclar las yemas de huevo con el resto de los ingredientes hasta que quede cremoso.

Ponga todo en una forma (forre con papel de hornear húmedo y use papel de aluminio en la parte inferior)
Pon 1 litro de agua en una bandeja para horno y calienta el horno a 140 °
Mete el bizcocho en el horno y hornea a 140 ° durante 1 hora
Luego aumente la temperatura a 175 ° durante 10-20 minutos
Apague el horno y abra un poco la puerta del horno (toalla / cuchara de madera)
Deje que el pastel se enfríe lentamente durante unos 10-15 minutos.
Luego sácalo y déjalo enfriar completamente

4 uova taglia M
2 cucchiai di farina tipo 405
1 cucchiaino di pasta di vaniglia (o 1 x zucchero vanigliato)
1 pizzico di sale


Preparazione:

Separare le uova e montare gli albumi con un po 'di zucchero (20-30 gr.) A neve ferma
Mescolare i tuorli con gli altri ingredienti fino a ottenere una crema
Ora piega con attenzione gli albumi
Metti tutto in una forma (fodera con carta da forno bagnata e usa un foglio di alluminio sul fondo)
Mettete 1 litro d'acqua su una teglia e scaldate il forno a 140 °
Mettete la torta in forno e infornate a 140 ° per 1 ora
Quindi aumentare la temperatura a 175 ° per 10-20 minuti
Spegnere il forno e aprire la porta del forno (asciugamano / cucchiaio di legno)
Lasciate raffreddare lentamente la torta per circa 10-15 minuti
Quindi estrarlo e lasciarlo raffreddare completamente

localizations.zh-SG.title: 為什麼這個芝士蛋糕比其他任何蛋糕都要好！ [食譜]
localizations.zh-SG.description:
這種芝士蛋糕配方是日本芝士蛋糕和西班牙芝士蛋糕之間的交叉。我曾經想嘗試一些新的東西，而這個芝士蛋糕是用它做的。多汁無止境，蓬鬆如日。

已經免費訂閱？ 👍：https：//tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
頻道支持：https：//www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
工藝品第二頻道：https：//www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

視頻中的杯子：https：//amzn.to/2JYofzm
烘烤釋放噴霧劑：https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe（以最便宜的方式，一切都一樣^^）
男士混音器：https://amzn.to/35izpag
博世攪拌機：https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

配料：

600克奶油芝士
400克奶油
200克糖
4個雞蛋大小M
2湯匙405型麵粉
1茶匙香草醬（或1 x香草糖）
1撮鹽


製備：

分離雞蛋，並用少許糖（20-30克）打碎蛋白。
將蛋黃與剩餘成分混合至奶油狀
現在小心地將蛋清折疊
將所有物品放入模具中（與濕烘焙紙對齊，並在底部使用鋁箔）
將1升水放在烤盤上，然後將烤箱加熱到140°
將蛋糕放入烤箱中，在140°烘烤1小時
然後將溫度升至175°10-20分鐘
關閉烤箱，然後打開烤箱門有裂痕（毛巾/木勺）
讓蛋糕慢慢冷卻約10-15分鐘
然後將其取出，使其完全冷卻

localizations.nl.title: Waarom deze cheesecake beter is dan alle andere! [RECEPT]
localizations.nl.description:
Dit cheesecake-recept is een kruising tussen een Japanse en een Spaanse cheesecake. Ik had ooit zin om iets nieuws te proberen en deze cheesecake is er van gemaakt. Sappig zonder einde en luchtig zoals de Japanners.

al gratis geabonneerd? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Kanaalondersteuning: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Handwerk tweede kanaal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

De mok uit de video: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Baking release spray: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (neem de goedkoopste, alles is toch hetzelfde ^^)
Men Mixer: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Bosch-mixer: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingrediënten:

600 gr Roomkaas
400 gr Room
200 gram suiker
4 eieren maat M
2 el bloem type 405
1 theelepel vanillepasta (of 1 x vanillesuiker)
1 snufje zout


Voorbereiding:

Scheid de eieren en klop de eiwitten met een beetje suiker (20-30 gr.) Stijf
Meng de eidooiers met de overige ingrediënten tot een romig geheel
Spatel nu voorzichtig het eiwit erdoor
Doe alles in een vorm (lijn met nat bakpapier en gebruik aluminiumfolie aan de onderkant)
Doe 1 liter water op een bakplaat en verwarm de oven tot 140 °
Zet de cake in de oven en bak 1 uur op 140 °
Verhoog vervolgens de temperatuur tot 175 ° gedurende 10-20 minuten
Schakel de oven uit en open de ovendeur een kier (handdoek / houten lepel)
Laat de cake ongeveer 10-15 minuten langzaam afkoelen
Haal het er dan uit en laat het volledig afkoelen

localizations.fr-FR.title: Pourquoi ce cheesecake est meilleur que tout autre! [RECETTE]
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Cette recette de cheesecake est un croisement entre un gâteau au fromage japonais et espagnol. Une fois, j'ai eu envie d'essayer quelque chose de nouveau et ce cheesecake en était fait. Juteux sans fin et moelleux comme les japonais.

déjà abonné gratuitement? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Prise en charge de la chaîne: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join

Le mug de la vidéo: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray anti-cuisson: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (prenez le moins cher, tout est pareil quand même ^^)
Mixeur hommes: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mélangeur Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingrédients:

600 gr. De fromage à la crème
400 gr de crème
200 grammes de sucre
4 œufs taille M
2 cuillères à soupe de farine type 405
1 cuillère à café de pâte de vanille (ou 1 x sucre vanillé)
1 pincée de sel


Préparation:

Séparez les œufs et battez les blancs d'œufs avec un peu de sucre (20-30 gr.) Jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient fermes
Mélanger les jaunes d'œufs avec le reste des ingrédients jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient crémeux
Maintenant, incorporer soigneusement les blancs d'œufs
Mettez le tout dans une forme (ligne avec du papier sulfurisé humide et utilisez une feuille d'aluminium en bas)
Mettre 1 litre d'eau sur une plaque à pâtisserie et chauffer le four à 140 °
Mettre le gâteau au four et cuire à 140 ° pendant 1 heure
Ensuite, augmentez la température à 175 ° pendant 10-20 minutes
Éteignez le four et ouvrez la porte du four une fissure (serviette / cuillère en bois)
Laissez le gâteau refroidir lentement pendant environ 10 à 15 minutes
Ensuite, retirez-le et laissez-le refroidir complètement

localizations.zh-HK.description:
這種芝士蛋糕配方是日本芝士蛋糕和西班牙芝士蛋糕之間的交叉。我曾經想嘗試一些新的東西，而這個芝士蛋糕是用它做的。多汁無止境，蓬鬆如日。

配料：

600克奶油芝士
400克奶油
200克糖
4個雞蛋大小M
2湯匙405型麵粉
1茶匙香草醬（或1 x香草糖）
1撮鹽


製備：

分離雞蛋，並用少許糖（20-30克）打碎蛋白。
將蛋黃與剩餘成分混合至奶油狀
現在小心地將蛋清折疊
將所有物品放入模具中（與濕烘焙紙對齊，並在底部使用鋁箔）
將1升水放在烤盤上，然後將烤箱加熱到140°
將蛋糕放入烤箱中，在140°烘烤1小時
然後將溫度升至175°10-20分鐘
關閉烤箱，然後打開烤箱門有裂痕（毛巾/木勺）
讓蛋糕慢慢冷卻約10-15分鐘
然後將其取出，使其完全冷卻

localizations.pt-PT.title: Por que este cheesecake é melhor do que qualquer outro! [RECEITA]
localizations.pt-PT.description:
Esta receita de cheesecake é um cruzamento entre um bolo de queijo japonês e um espanhol. Uma vez tive vontade de experimentar algo novo e este cheesecake foi feito com isso. Suculento sem fim e fofo como o japonês.

já se inscreveu gratuitamente? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88

Spray de liberação de cozimento: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (pegue o mais barato, tudo é igual de qualquer maneira ^^)

Mixer Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredientes:

600 gr de cream cheese
400 gr. Creme
200 gramas de açucar
4 ovos tamanho M
2 colheres de sopa de farinha tipo 405
1 colher de chá de pasta de baunilha (ou 1 x açúcar de baunilha)
1 pitada de sal


Preparação:

Separe os ovos e bata as claras com um pouco de açúcar (20-30 gr.) Até ficarem firmes
Misture as gemas com os ingredientes restantes até ficar cremoso
Agora, envolva cuidadosamente as claras em neve
Coloque tudo em uma forma (forre com papel manteiga e use papel alumínio no fundo)
Coloque 1 litro de água em uma assadeira e aqueça o forno a 140 °
Coloque o bolo no forno e leve ao forno a 140 ° por 1 hora
Em seguida, aumente a temperatura para 175 ° por 10-20 minutos
Desligue o forno e abra a porta do forno uma fresta (toalha / colher de pau)
Deixe o bolo esfriar lentamente por cerca de 10-15 minutos
Em seguida, retire e deixe esfriar completamente

localizations.no.description:
Denne ostekakeoppskriften er et kryss mellom en japansk og en spansk ostekake. Jeg hadde en gang lyst til å prøve noe nytt, og denne ostekaken ble laget av den. Saftig uten ende og luftig som japanerne.

Ingredienser:

600 gr. Kremost
400 gr. Krem
200 gram sukker
4 egg størrelse M
2 ss mel type 405
1 ts vanilje pasta (eller 1 x vaniljesukker)
1 klype salt


Forberedelse:

Skill eggene og pisk eggehvitene med litt sukker (20-30 gr.) Til stivhet
Bland eggeplommene med de resterende ingrediensene til de er kremete
Brett nå eggehvitene forsiktig inn
Ha alt i en form (stryk med vått bakepapir og bruk aluminiumsfolie i bunnen)
Ha 1 liter vann på et bakeplate og varm ovnen til 140 °
Sett kaken i ovnen og stek på 140 ° i 1 time
Øk deretter temperaturen til 175 ° i 10-20 minutter
Slå av ovnen og åpne ovnsdøren en sprekk (håndkle / treskje)
La kaken avkjøles sakte i ca 10-15 minutter

已經免費訂閱？ 👍：https：//tinyurl.com/y82tkl88

配料：

600克奶油芝士
400克奶油
200克糖
4個雞蛋大小M
2湯匙405型麵粉
1茶匙香草醬（或1 x香草糖）
1撮鹽


製備：

分離雞蛋，並用少許糖（20-30克）打碎蛋白。
將蛋黃與剩餘成分混合至奶油狀

關閉烤箱，然後打開烤箱門有裂痕（毛巾/木勺）

localizations.uk.description:
Цей рецепт чізкейка - це щось середнє між японським та іспанським сирним пирогом. Одного разу мені захотілося спробувати щось нове, і цей чізкейк з нього зробили. Соковита без кінця і пухнаста, як японська.

Змішувач Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Інгредієнти:

600 гр. Плавлений сир
400 гр. Вершки
200 грам цукру
4 яйця розміром M
2 ст. Ложки борошна типу 405
1 чайна ложка ванільної пасти (або 1 х ванільний цукор)
1 щіпка солі


Підготовка:

Відокремте яйця і збийте білки з невеликою кількістю цукру (20-30 гр.) До стійкості
Змішайте жовтки з рештою інгредієнтів до стану крему
Тепер акуратно складіть білки
Викладіть все у форму (застеліть вологим папером для випічки, а внизу використовуйте алюмінієву фольгу)
Покладіть 1 літр води на деко і розігрійте духовку до 140 °
Поставте пиріг у духовку і випікайте при 140 ° протягом 1 години
Потім збільште температуру до 175 ° протягом 10-20 хвилин
Вимкніть піч і відкрийте дверцята духовки на щілині (рушник / дерев'яна ложка)
Дайте пирогу повільно охолонути приблизно 10-15 хвилин
Потім дістаньте його і дайте йому повністю охолонути

localizations.fr-CA.title: Pourquoi ce cheesecake est meilleur que tout autre! [RECETTE]
localizations.fr-CA.description:
Cette recette de cheesecake est un croisement entre un gâteau au fromage japonais et espagnol. Une fois, j'ai eu envie d'essayer quelque chose de nouveau et ce cheesecake en était fait. Juteux sans fin et moelleux comme les japonais.

déjà abonné gratuitement? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Prise en charge de la chaîne: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Artisanat deuxième canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

Le mug de la vidéo: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray anti-cuisson: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (prenez le moins cher, tout est pareil quand même ^^)
Mixeur hommes: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mélangeur Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingrédients:

600 gr. De fromage à la crème
400 gr de crème
200 grammes de sucre
4 œufs taille M
2 cuillères à soupe de farine type 405
1 cuillère à café de pâte de vanille (ou 1 x sucre vanillé)
1 pincée de sel


Préparation:

Séparez les œufs et battez les blancs d'œufs avec un peu de sucre (20-30 gr.) Jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient fermes
Mélanger les jaunes d'œufs avec le reste des ingrédients jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient crémeux
Maintenant, incorporer soigneusement les blancs d'œufs
Mettez le tout dans une forme (ligne avec du papier sulfurisé humide et utilisez une feuille d'aluminium en bas)
Mettre 1 litre d'eau sur une plaque à pâtisserie et chauffer le four à 140 °
Mettre le gâteau au four et cuire à 140 ° pendant 1 heure
Ensuite, augmentez la température à 175 ° pendant 10-20 minutes
Éteignez le four et ouvrez la porte du four une fissure (serviette / cuillère en bois)
Laissez le gâteau refroidir lentement pendant environ 10 à 15 minutes
Ensuite, retirez-le et laissez-le refroidir complètement

Ингредиенты:

600 гр. Сливочный сыр
400 гр. Сливки
200 грамм сахара
4 яйца размером M
2 ст.ложки муки сорта 405
1 чайная ложка ванильной пасты (или 1 ванильный сахар)
1 щепотка соли


Подготовка:

Разделите яйца и взбейте яичные белки с небольшим количеством сахара (20-30 гр.), Пока они не станут густыми.
Смешайте яичные желтки с остальными ингредиентами до кремообразного состояния.
Теперь аккуратно добавляем яичные белки.
Выложите все в форму (выстелите влажной бумагой для выпечки и используйте алюминиевую фольгу внизу)
Налейте на противень 1 л воды и разогрейте духовку до 140 °.
Поставить лепешку в духовку и выпекать при 140 ° 1 час.
Затем увеличьте температуру до 175 ° на 10-20 минут.
Выключите духовку и приоткройте дверцу духовки (полотенцем / деревянной ложкой)
Дайте пирогу медленно остыть примерно 10-15 минут.
Затем выньте его и дайте полностью остыть

localizations.zh-Hans.title: 为什么这个芝士蛋糕比其他任何蛋糕都要好！ [食谱]
localizations.zh-Hans.description:
这种芝士蛋糕配方是日本芝士蛋糕和西班牙芝士蛋糕之间的交叉。我曾经想尝试一些新的东西，而这个芝士蛋糕是用它做的。多汁无止境，蓬松如日文。

已经免费订阅？ 👍：https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
频道支持：https：//www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join

男士混音器：https://amzn.to/35izpag
博世搅拌机：https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

配料：

600克奶油芝士
400克奶油
200克糖
4个鸡蛋大小M
2汤匙405型面粉
1茶匙香草酱（或1 x香草糖）
1撮盐


制备：

分离鸡蛋，并用少许糖（20-30克）打成蛋清，直到变硬
将蛋黄与剩余成分混合至奶油状
现在小心地将蛋清折叠
将所有物品放入模具中（与湿烘焙纸对齐，并在底部使用铝箔）
将1升水放在烤盘上，然后将烤箱加热到140°
将蛋糕放入烤箱，在140°烘烤1小时
然后将温度升至175°10-20分钟
关闭烤箱，然后打开烤箱门有裂痕（毛巾/木勺）
让蛋糕慢慢冷却约10-15分钟
然后将其取出，使其完全冷却

localizations.fr-BE.title: Pourquoi ce cheesecake est meilleur que tout autre! [RECETTE]
localizations.fr-BE.description:
Cette recette de cheesecake est un croisement entre un gâteau au fromage japonais et espagnol. Une fois, j'ai eu envie d'essayer quelque chose de nouveau et ce cheesecake en était fait. Juteux sans fin et moelleux comme les japonais.

déjà abonné gratuitement? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Prise en charge de la chaîne: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Artisanat deuxième canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

Le mug de la vidéo: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray anti-cuisson: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (prenez le moins cher, tout est pareil quand même ^^)
Mixeur hommes: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mélangeur Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingrédients:

600 gr. De fromage à la crème
400 gr de crème
200 grammes de sucre
4 œufs taille M
2 cuillères à soupe de farine type 405
1 cuillère à café de pâte de vanille (ou 1 x sucre vanillé)
1 pincée de sel


Préparation:

Séparez les œufs et battez les blancs d'œufs avec un peu de sucre (20-30 gr.) Jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient fermes
Mélanger les jaunes d'œufs avec le reste des ingrédients jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient crémeux
Maintenant, incorporer soigneusement les blancs d'œufs
Mettez le tout dans une forme (ligne avec du papier sulfurisé humide et utilisez une feuille d'aluminium en bas)
Mettre 1 litre d'eau sur une plaque à pâtisserie et chauffer le four à 140 °
Mettre le gâteau au four et cuire à 140 ° pendant 1 heure
Ensuite, augmentez la température à 175 ° pendant 10-20 minutes
Éteignez le four et ouvrez la porte du four une fissure (serviette / cuillère en bois)
Laissez le gâteau refroidir lentement pendant environ 10 à 15 minutes
Ensuite, retirez-le et laissez-le refroidir complètement

Υποστήριξη καναλιού: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Δεύτερο κανάλι χειροτεχνίας: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

Η κούπα από το βίντεο: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Σπρέι απελευθέρωσης ψησίματος: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (πάρτε το φθηνότερο, όλα είναι τα ίδια ούτως ή άλλως ^^)
Ανδρικό μίξερ: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Bosch Mixer: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Συστατικά:

600 γρ. Τυρί κρέμας
400 γρ. Κρέμα
200 γραμμάρια ζάχαρης
4 αυγά μέγεθος Μ
2 κουταλιές της σούπας αλεύρι τύπου 405
1 κουταλάκι του γλυκού πάστα βανίλιας (ή 1 x ζάχαρη βανίλιας)
1 πρέζα αλάτι


Παρασκευή:

Διαχωρίστε τα αυγά και κτυπήστε το ασπράδι με λίγη ζάχαρη (20-30 γρ.) Μέχρι να σκληρύνει
Ανακατέψτε τους κρόκους των αυγών με τα υπόλοιπα συστατικά έως ότου κρεμώσουν
Τώρα διπλώστε προσεκτικά τα ασπράδια των αυγών
Βάλτε τα πάντα σε φόρμα (ευθυγραμμίστε με υγρό χαρτί ψησίματος και χρησιμοποιήστε αλουμινόχαρτο στο κάτω μέρος)
Βάλτε 1 λίτρο νερό σε ένα ταψί και θερμάνετε το φούρνο στους 140 °
Βάζουμε το κέικ στο φούρνο και ψήνουμε στους 140 ° για 1 ώρα
Στη συνέχεια, αυξήστε τη θερμοκρασία στους 175 ° για 10-20 λεπτά
Σβήστε το φούρνο και ανοίξτε την πόρτα του φούρνου μια ρωγμή (πετσέτα / ξύλινο κουτάλι)
Αφήστε το κέικ να κρυώσει αργά για περίπου 10-15 λεπτά
Στη συνέχεια βγάλτε το και αφήστε το να κρυώσει εντελώς

localizations.da.title: Hvorfor denne ostekage er bedre end nogen anden! [OPSKRIFT]
localizations.da.description:
Denne ostekageopskrift er en krydsning mellem en japansk og en spansk ostekage. Jeg havde engang lyst til at prøve noget nyt, og denne ostekage blev lavet af det. Saftig uden ende og fluffy som japanerne.

abonnerer du allerede gratis? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Kanalsupport: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Håndværk anden kanal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

Kruset fra videoen: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Baking release spray: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (tag det billigste, alt er alligevel det samme ^^)
Mænds mixer: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Bosch mixer: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredienser:

600 gr. Flødeost
400 gr. Fløde
200 gram sukker
4 æg størrelse M
2 spsk mel type 405
1 tsk vanilje pasta (eller 1 x vaniljesukker)
1 knivspids salt


Forberedelse:

Adskil æggene og pisk æggehviderne med lidt sukker (20-30 gr.) Indtil de er stive
Bland æggeblommer med de resterende ingredienser, indtil de er cremede
Fold forsigtigt æggehviderne ind
Sæt alt i en form (stryg med vådt bagepapir og brug aluminiumsfolie i bunden)
Sæt 1 liter vand på et bageplade, og opvarm ovnen til 140 °
Sæt kagen i ovnen og bages ved 140 ° i 1 time
Forøg derefter temperaturen til 175 ° i 10-20 minutter
Sluk for ovnen og åbn ovndøren en revne (håndklæde / træske)
Lad kagen afkøle langsomt i ca. 10-15 minutter
Tag det derefter ud og lad det køle helt ned

localizations.es-MX.title: ¡Por qué esta tarta de queso es mejor que cualquier otra! [RECETA]
localizations.es-MX.description:
Esta receta de tarta de queso es un cruce entre una tarta de queso japonesa y una española. Una vez tuve ganas de probar algo nuevo y esta tarta de queso estaba hecha con eso. Jugoso sin fin y esponjoso como los japoneses.

¿Ya estás suscrito gratis? 👍: https://tinyurl.com/y82tkl88
Soporte de canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBHE4pG06XYrad-l5hwWYpg/join
Segundo canal de artesanía: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7WeWHtHZ1FdVtGAdD-JNxw

La taza del video: https://amzn.to/2JYofzm
Spray de liberación para hornear: https://amzn.to/3nbiGfe (toma el más barato, todo es igual de todos modos ^^)
Mezclador de hombres: https://amzn.to/35izpag
Mezclador Bosch: https://amzn.to/3n8TEgA

Ingredientes:

600 gr. De queso crema
400 gr. De nata
200 gramos de azucar
4 huevos talla M
2 cucharadas de harina tipo 405
1 cucharadita de pasta de vainilla (o 1 x azúcar de vainilla)
1 pizca de sal


Preparación:

Separar los huevos y batir la clara con un poco de azúcar (20-30 gr.) Hasta que quede rígida
Mezclar las yemas de huevo con el resto de los ingredientes hasta que quede cremoso.
Ahora doble con cuidado las claras de huevo
Ponga todo en una forma (forre con papel de hornear húmedo y use papel de aluminio en la parte inferior)
Pon 1 litro de agua en una bandeja para horno y calienta el horno a 140 °
Mete el bizcocho en el horno y hornea a 140 ° durante 1 hora
Luego aumente la temperatura a 175 ° durante 10-20 minutos
Apague el horno y abra un poco la puerta del horno (toalla / cuchara de madera)
Deje que el pastel se enfríe lentamente durante unos 10-15 minutos.
Luego sácalo y déjalo enfriar completamente

snippet.title: Köstliche Reise! Wer backt die beste Tarte? | Die Verkostung | Das große Backen 2020 | SAT.1
snippet.description:
In der zweiten Runde der 8. Staffel "Das große Backen" schicken wir unsere Hobbybäcker auf eine köstliche Reise durch das wunderschöne Frankreich. Das Ursprungsland der Patisserié hält drei knifflige Aufgaben für die Kandidaten bereit. Wer kann dem Druck standhalten und wer muss diese Woche leider das Backzelt verlassen?

#DasGroßeBacken #SAT1

Alle Rezepte gibt’s hier: https://s71.link/b/351xFAn 
Das Große Backen auf Instagram: https://s71.link/b/3cPkzJv

Alle Videos von 2014 in einer Playlist: https://s71.link/b/3awzTZF 
Alle Videos von 2013 in einer Playlist: https://s71.link/b/2VOzaxO 

Mehr zur Sendung: https://s71.link/b/3cMy3FR 

Bei „Das große Backen“ sucht SAT.1 wieder „Deutschlands besten Hobbybäcker“: Zehn Kandidaten aus ganz Deutschland stellen sich der Jury! Die Juroren Christian Hümbs, mehrfach ausgezeichnet als Patissier des Jahres, und Bettina Schliephake-Burchardt, Konditormeisterin und gefeierte Tortendekorateurin erwarten von den zehn Kandidaten vor allem eines: absolute Höchstleistungen. Dem Gewinner winken ein eigenes Backbuch und 10.000 Euro Preisgeld. 

Auch die Moderatorin ist Fans der Koch-Show bereits bekannt: Enie van de Meiklokjes. Die leidenschaftliche Hobbybäckerin führt bereits seit Staffel 1 durch die Sendung.

snippet.title: Apple's M1 Mac is not what you think...
snippet.description:
The first Apple Silicon Macs are here sporting the new M1 SoC. What does it mean for Macs today and into the future? Let's find out!
Sign up for Setapp today! https://setapp.com/?utm_source=snazzylabs&utm_campaign=apps&utm_medium=sponsorship

Check out my gear/suggestions! - http://amazon.com/shop/snazzylabs

Subscribe to my podcast Flashback! - http://relay.fm/flashback
Follow me on Twitter - http://twitter.com/snazzyq
Follow me on Instagram - http://instagram.com/snazzyq

At long last, Apple has finally announced and will soon be releasing Arm-based Macs based on Apple's new "Apple Silicon" family. This new chip, the M1, is based on the A14 and makes its way to the MacBook Air, 13" MacBook Pro with Touch Bar, and Mac mini. Specs are vague and performance is yet to be determined, but if Apple's slides are to be believed, this chip design and these machines are just the beginning of a hugely important transition for Apple and computing in general. But let's go beyond what Apple said in the keynote and dive into some of the nuance behind this new Apple Silicon M1 chip.

snippet.title: Bos Entscheidung: Toni oder Maurice? ❤️🤔  | Köln 50667 #1991
snippet.description:
Während Bo von Maurice ein romantisches Date organisiert bekommt, kann sie auch diesmal ihre Sorge um Toni nicht vergessen. Das geht Maurice ziemlich gegen den Strich. Zieht er jetzt den Schlussstrich? 

Abonniert unseren Kanal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnrvUg5MJWPDSrv_voT7AqA?sub_confirmation=1
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/koeln50667
Schaut euch die kompletten Folgen auf TVNOW an: http://www.tvnow.de/rtl2/koeln-50667
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/koeln50667
Twitter: http://twitter.com/rtl2

„Köln 50667“ ist eine Reality-Soap, die seit 2013 täglich von montags bis freitags im Vorabendprogramm gesendet wird. Aufgrund des großen Erfolges wurde die ursprünglich auf 120 Folgen begrenzte Serie weiter produziert und ist bisher auf über 1700 Folgen angewachsen. Im Mittelpunkt stehen unter anderem Kevin, Jan, Sophia, Marc und Mel. "Köln 50667" erzählt die spannenden Geschichten von Kevin, Sophia und Co. Egal, ob im Cage oder in den WGs - hier gibt es Leben pur.

snippet.title: Das neue Karnevalstrikot des 1. FC Köln | Karneval | 11.11. |  Bleibt zu Hause | EFFZEH
snippet.description:
🤡 Kein Bützchen, kein Schunkeln, kein Singen: Die Jecken müssen an diesem Elften im Elften auf vieles verzichten – aber nicht aufs FC-Karnevalstrikot. Das Trikot im Lappenclown-Look ist ab sofort erhältlich.
